How It Works

At AUTOBOLI LTD, we’ve made accessing auction data simple and straightforward. Here’s how you can get started and make the most of our service in just a few easy steps.

Sign Up

Visit our website and choose a subscription plan that best fits your needs—Silver, Gold, or Platinum. Each plan offers unique benefits to help you access and make the most of our real-time auction data. Signing up is quick and easy, and your subscription begins immediately upon completion of the registration process.

Take the first step towards transforming the way you navigate the auction market with AUTOBOLI LTD.

Access Real-Time Auction Data

Once you’ve signed up, you’ll have instant access to auction data from all over the UK. Our platform offers real-time updates on auction listings, so you can see what’s available as soon as it’s up for grabs. You can also filter auctions by region, vehicle type, or auction house, helping you find exactly what you need.

Use the Data to Make Smart Decisions

Our data includes key information such as:

Auction Location and Time
Vehicle Make, Model, and Year
Vehicle Conditions and detailed descriptions
Bidding Prices and auction results

With this data at your fingertips, you can track market trends, identify the best deals, and make informed buying decisions. We also provide basic and advanced analytics (available in our Gold and Platinum plans) to help you forecast trends and optimize your strategy.

Stay Informed with Alerts

To make things even easier, you can set up custom alerts based on your preferences. Get notified about new listings, price drops, or upcoming auctions that match your criteria. This ensures you never miss an opportunity.

Subscription Billing

Your subscription begins immediately upon completion of the registration process. Payments are processed monthly:

If you sign up after the 1st of the month, you will be charged a prorated amount for the remaining days of the month.

Moving forward, all subscriptions will be charged on the 1st day of each month via direct debit.

Customer Support

If you have any questions or need assistance, our customer support team is always available to help. Our Gold and Platinum subscribers also benefit from priority support for faster response times.

Cancel Anytime

You can cancel your subscription at any time. If you choose to cancel, you will still have access to the service until the end of your billing cycle. There are no hidden fees or penalties.

With AUTOBOLI LTD, getting auction data has never been easier. We provide you with all the tools and information you need to stay competitive in the automotive market.

Let's Start Accessing Exclusive Auction Data Today!

Don’t miss out on the best deals. Join our community of smart bidders and unlock full access to auction listings.

Get Started

Gain insights into thousands of vehicle auctions and make smarter bidding decisions. Subscribe to access full auction data across the nation.
